{"tid":1717344,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"哇搞咩 市中心停哂電嘅","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T23:48:36.000Z","uid":51382,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0943b70d2c9b940e9f755afbe865adec233b9818","tid":1717344,"uid":51382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sSaJPAvelYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsSaJPAvelYM&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4eyzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=ee3b38b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sSaJPAvelYM</a><br />\n<br />\n係咪班綠色曱甴暴徒整<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a89381ed5dc21d78a55451ce9050dce21605470","tid":1717344,"uid":312125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abpOQ16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabpOQ16.png&h=1a9ab24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHwOww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHwOww.jpg&h=056adf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JerhLyH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJerhLyH.png&h=a8e9db0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"06e771e99896192cf08f4d1811e31ddd01d97fe0","tid":1717344,"uid":497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"咩位置?"},{"pid":"46d865c18078f527cd5f0a341780ce46b5165252","tid":1717344,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06e771e99896192cf08f4d1811e31ddd01d97fe0","tid":1717344,"uid":497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"咩位置?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"係唔係葵芳？<br />\n警署果邊？"},{"pid":"6dcd02a0bc0cd6c1514217b691e293aa8cd74355","tid":1717344,"uid":94167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:59:23.000Z","msg":"屯市"},{"pid":"884607ab199292156b5519268886f19e23117b4c","tid":1717344,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:03:54.000Z","msg":"現場手足要極度小心.  因住敵人乘夜狂攻."},{"pid":"13b78d33d435873421af95a1567d3157378c7751","tid":1717344,"uid":51382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"屯門 青山天主教小學 vcity附近"},{"pid":"ba9d7815c38a2b0e359ba70ecec933e94688a875","tid":1717344,"uid":51382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:16:26.000Z","msg":"點解冇新聞講？"},{"pid":"4faaae03d9b26002f872bcbaa975932b5cb503de","tid":1717344,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"今晚好鬼"},{"pid":"525ed033af437289230b3ad121c8bf277ab0b2c8","tid":1717344,"uid":36470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:20:40.000Z","msg":"小心"},{"pid":"67cb83a039abda0419e